The paper deals with video captioning and character recognition, which are primarily computer vision and natural language processing tasks. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) and cs.CL (Computation and Language) are the most likely sub-categories. Additionally, the paper involves multimodal architectures and dataset creation, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper also involves semi-automatic annotation procedures, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
